articles.title: UK Woman Marries Herself In Unique Celebration, Ending The Wait For 'Mr Right' - NDTV
articles.description: Ms Wilkinson said that she splashed out 10,000 pounds (Rs 10,11,421) on the celebration after saving each month and adding any extra windfalls she had, such as bingo wins.
articles.content:
The woman saved up 20 years for her dream wedding, only to marry herself.
